(761, 'Registro criado', 1, 'App\\Models\\NotumInf#1', 1, NULL, '{\"escola_id\":\"4\",\"turma_id\":\"4\",\"disciplina_id\":\"5\",\"aluno_id\":\"8\",\"conhecendo_contexto\":\"Assim se descobriu que existiam quatro grupos lingu\\u00edsticos principais, sendo eles: os tupi-guarani, os cara\\u00edba, os macro-j\\u00ea e os arauaque. Desses troncos lingu\\u00edsticos, como tamb\\u00e9m s\\u00e3o chamados, derivam uma s\\u00e9rie de grupos \\u00e9tnicos e varia\\u00e7\\u00f5es lingu\\u00edsticas que d\\u00e3o origem aos idiomas ind\\u00edgenas modernos.\",\"registro_conquistas\":\"Com a chegada dos jesu\\u00edtas, em meados do s\\u00e9culo XVI, uma s\\u00e9rie de \\u201cobras gramaticais\\u201d foi produzida com o objetivo de normatizar algumas \\u201cl\\u00ednguas dificultosas\\u201d da col\\u00f4nia. Nesse empreendimento, foram catalogados conhecimentos valiosos sobre l\\u00ednguas ind\\u00edgenas do per\\u00edodo que corresponde \\u00e0 chegada dos portugueses \\u00e0 Am\\u00e9rica.\",\"01EO01_s1\":\"1\",\"01EO01_s2\":\"1\",\"01EO02_s1\":\"1\",\"01EO02_s2\":\"1\",\"01EO03_s1\":\"1\",\"01EO03_s2\":\"1\",\"01EO04_s1\":\"1\",\"01EO04_s2\":\"1\",\"01EO05_s1\":\"1\",\"01EO05_s2\":\"1\",\"01EO06_s1\":\"1\",\"01EO06_s2\":\"1\",\"01EO07_s1\":\"1\",\"01EO07_s2\":\"1\",\"02EO01_s1\":\"1\",\"02EO01_s2\":\"1\",\"02EO02_s1\":\"1\",\"02EO02_s2\":\"1\",\"02EO03_s1\":\"1\",\"02EO03_s2\":\"1\",\"02EO04_s1\":\"1\",\"02EO04_s2\":\"1\",\"02EO05_s1\":\"1\",\"02EO05_s2\":\"1\",\"02EO06_s1\":\"1\",\"02EO06_s2\":\"1\",\"02EO07_s1\":\"1\",\"02EO07_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET01_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET01_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET02_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET02_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET03_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET03_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET04_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET04_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET05_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET05_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET06_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET06_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET07_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET07_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET08_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET08_s2\":\"1\",\"01ET09_s1\":\"1\",\"01ET09_s2\":\"1\",\"02ET01_s1\":\"1\",\"02ET01_s2\":\"1\",\"02ET02_s1\":\"1\",\"02ET02_s2\":\"1\",\"0